q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4snk17zq&h=1f81444c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q6zhy9ts\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq6zhy9ts&h=e779051f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a759873060c477e3fcb54460b7ed236ec0861d43","tid":248702,"uid":29431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以為你講邊套催履奇緣，原來講西遊記。<br />\n<br />\n附近咪有西夏王陵，呢度都有取景<br />\n<br />\n賀蘭山岩畫<br />\n<br />\n石嘴山沙湖，呢度都好似有取景，鄭中基果套就肯定有。</blockquote><br />\n係呀,好想感受下苦海翻起愛恨既感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知有啲位仲有無KEEP 著。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4snk17zq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4snk17zq&h=1f81444c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q6zhy9ts\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq6zhy9ts&h=e779051f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打使左幾錢?<br />\n去個d位係咪有旅遊車?定一定要包車?"},{"pid":"aa12505a60ba103c832e0fce93b3293390e67821","tid":248702,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以為你講邊套催履奇緣，原來講西遊記。<br />\n<br />\n附近咪有西夏王陵，呢度都有取景<br />\n<br />\n賀蘭山岩畫<br />\n<br />\n石嘴山沙湖，呢度都好似有取景，鄭中基果套就肯定有。</blockquote><br />\n係呀,好想感受下苦海翻起愛恨既感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知有啲位仲有無KEEP 著。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4snk17zq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4snk17zq&h=1f81444c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q6zhy9ts\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq6zhy9ts&h=e779051f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打使左幾錢?<br />\n去個d位係咪有旅遊車?定一定要包車?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n洗幾錢答你唔到了，太耐既事<br />\n<br />\n鎮北堡個電影城係有巴士可以由市中心過去。<br />\n<br />\n但賀蘭山岩畫、西夏王陵係包咗部小麵包車，以前嚟講唔貴，因為果邊啲車行天然氣，天然氣平到笑，開成日車見佢入天然氣入咗十幾蚊咁大把。<br />\n<br />\n因為我果陣仲諗着落敦煌，所以無去沙坡頭同中衛。<br />\n<br />\n銀川，我去果陣深圳係無直飛，依家深圳都有機去了。<br />\n<br />\n不過我係全程火車，廣州去內蒙，由內蒙再玩番落去，好多都係硬座或無座。"},{"pid":"3ff4eef4d5e72b4270d3f88940d4d019b38a7037","tid":248702,"uid":108280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"可以去下騰格里沙漠<br />\n同青銅峽108塔 <br />\n<br />\n唔好去西夏王陵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c008d3f885bc7f389f7f4a0bd0aa16ecf1a3faa","tid":248702,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去下騰格里沙漠<br />\n同青銅峽108塔 <br />\n<br />\n唔好去西夏王陵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主要去尋西遊記，一定要去西夏王陵喎。<br />\n<br />\n智尊寶，唔記得係紫霞定白骨仙佢哋同牛魔王開拖就喺西夏王陵。<br />\n<br />\n當然可以話冇乜文物睇，所有西夏黑水城文物都去晒俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n聖彼得堡 Hermitage Museum 亞洲區館，有展覽部份有西夏文字嘅文獻同碑文。<br />\n<br />\n仲要果邊啲學者串鳩班留學生，佢哋有西夏嘅文物，你哋反而冇。"},{"pid":"547b6105711cbf954cbe22507a73bd1a6200b327","tid":248702,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"正呀"},{"pid":"e86d3d21b353b9a95c99bff79d2a319675b83922","tid":248702,"uid":29431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以為你講邊套催履奇緣，原來講西遊記。<br />\n<br />\n附近咪有西夏王陵，呢度都有取景<br />\n<br />\n賀蘭山岩畫<br />\n<br />\n石嘴山沙湖，呢度都好似有取景，鄭中基果套就肯定有。</blockquote><br />\n係呀,好想感受下苦海翻起愛恨既感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔知有啲位仲有無KEEP 著。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4snk17zq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4snk17zq&h=1f81444c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q6zhy9ts\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq6zhy9ts&h=e779051f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打使左幾錢?<br />\n去個d位係咪有旅遊車?定一定要包車?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n洗幾錢答你唔到了，太耐既事<br />\n<br />\n鎮北堡個電影城係有巴士可以由市中心過去。<br />\n<br />\n但賀蘭山岩畫、西夏王陵係包咗部小麵包車，以前嚟講唔貴，因為果邊啲車行天然氣，天然氣平到笑，開成日車見佢入天然氣入咗十幾蚊咁大把。<br />\n<br />\n因為我果陣仲諗着落敦煌，所以無去沙坡頭同中衛。<br />\n<br />\n銀川，我去果陣深圳係無直飛，依家深圳都有機去了。<br />\n<br />\n不過我係全程火車，廣州去內蒙，由內蒙再玩番落去，好多都係硬座或無座。</blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊坐火車去定飛機,睇睇下可以去埋張掖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}